These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, aquamarine, black
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes black is the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Color   | fuchsia | aquamarine | black   |
| Transport      | motorbike    | roller  | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, light-blue, blue
There 3 different types of food: zucchini, potato, kiwi
1. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
2. the person eating potato is on the far left##1
3. the person eating potato is the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Color      | light-blue | coral     | blue      |
| Food   | potato | zucchini | kiwi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, reading, card-games
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, sports, disaster
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | sudoku | card-games  | reading       |
| Movie-Genre       | action     | sports | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, techno, punk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, pall-mall, aristoff
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Music-Genre    | punk    | techno     | electronic |
| Cigar   | aristoff | alhambra | pall-mall     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, white, light-blue
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, march, july
1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who likes purple is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Color         | white | purple     | light-blue |
| Birthday   | july        | june | march    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, egyptian, mexican
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, swimming, cycling
1. the malaysian is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the mexican is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Nationality        | mexican | malaysian      | egyptian  |
| Sport   | sailing       | swimming | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, january, may
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, teacher, scientist
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is the teacher##1
3. the bartender is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Birthday   | may      | june     | january    |
| Job           | bartender | scientist | teacher |

