.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, amber, ebony
3 different games are played: billiard, bridge, chess
1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person playing chess##1
3. the person who likes amber is the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Color    | ebony | chestnut | amber      |
| Game   | billiard     | chess | bridge |

