.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dunhill, blend
City: boston, marseilles, liverpool
1. the person traveling to boston is the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Cigar   | blend | dunhill | aristoff  |
| City     | liverpool     | boston      | marseilles |

