.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, turkish, spanish
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, airplane, car
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the turkish##1
2. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Nationality      | australian   | turkish    | spanish    |
| Transport   | airplane | ship | car |

