.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, surfing, basketball
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, romance, crime
1. the person who's sport is basketball is the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Sport   | handball | basketball   | surfing  |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | documentary | romance |

