.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-12::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, spinach, nectarine
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, water
1. the person eating asparagus is in the middle##1
2. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Food   | nectarine    | asparagus     | spinach   |
| Beverage   | juice | fanta | water |

