.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
City: london, nizza, boston
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, june, july
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to boston is in the middle##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| City   | london     | boston   | nizza     |
| Birthday    | july | june | october |

