.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, mauve, black
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, 7up, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
3. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Color   | coral    | black | mauve |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | almond-milk     | 7up        |

