.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
3 different games are played: go, canasta, whist
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, roller, skateboard
1. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Game      | go  | whist | canasta  |
| Transport   | roller | skateboard   | airplane |

