1. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1
2. the thai is on the right of the japanese##1
3. the japanese is on the left of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Nationality   | japanese | thai | french    |
| Color        | pink    | coral | turquise |

