.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, fonseca, old-henry
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, fishing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Cigar           | fonseca | old-henry | tiparillo |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks  | singing      | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, chinchilla, mouse
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, chef, librarian
1. the librarian is on the right of the security-guard##1
2. the owner of the frog is the librarian##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Pet    | chinchilla | mouse   | frog        |
| Job   | chef    | security-guard | librarian |

