.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, fisherman, security-guard
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, german, chinese
1. the german is in the middle##1
2. the chinese is on the left of the paramedic##1
3. the fisherman is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Job    | security-guard | paramedic       | fisherman  |
| Nationality   | chinese  | german | brazilian |

 